        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/portuguese-prime-minister-luis-montenegro-debate-confidence-motion-vote-lisbon-parliament.png" alt="Portuguese Prime Minister Luis Montenegro gestures during a debate preceding a confidence motion vote at the Portuguese parliament in Lisbon" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
